    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Directions"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a>This is one of the most important smoothie recipes for you!"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a>It's delicious and the most effective tool in detoxing heavy metals from your brain, liver, other organs and your whole body. I find it very easy to consume all of those detoxing ingredients at the same time in a smoothie, but if you're not a smoothie person and you still need to get rid of heavy metals (tbh most of us do!) then make sure you consume all of those foods in one day. Especially the five key ingredients: Wild blueberries, fresh coriander greens/stalks, Atlantic dulse, barley grass juice powder and spirulina. Please look for Barley grass juice powder and not just barley grass powder, there's a big difference."
    },
